OL,3,CMan who locked woman in his home
OL,4,Cbefore sexually assaulting her jailed
OL,6,FA man who locked a woman in his home
OL,7,Fbefore attacking and sexually
OL,8,Fassaulting her has been jailed for
OL,9,Fmore than a decade.
OL,11,FLiam Maughan, 37, invited the woman
OL,12,Fover to his address in North Tyneside
OL,13,Fin November 2022 before locking her
OL,14,Finside.
OL,16,FUnprepared to let her go, Maughan
OL,17,Fstrangled the victim and assaulted her
OL,18,Fusing a skipping rope until she passed
OL,19,Fout, Northumbria Police said.
