OL,3,CMan who locked woman in his home
OL,4,Cbefore sexually assaulting her jailed
OL,6,FThe force said he then forced her to
OL,7,Fperform sexual acts, without her
OL,8,Fconsent while threatening to kill her.
OL,10,FThe terrified woman eventually managed
OL,11,Fto flee from the address, seeking
OL,12,Frefuge in a nearby house.
OL,14,FShe reported the incident to police
OL,15,Fand Maughan, of Marina View, Wallsend,
OL,16,Fwas arrested and charged with a string
OL,17,Fof offences.
OL,19,FHe initially denied the allegations,
OL,20,Fclaiming the sexual acts, and other
OL,21,Fsubsequent events, were consensual.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
