OL,3,CMan who locked woman in his home
OL,4,Cbefore sexually assaulting her jailed
OL,6,FHowever, in March, Maughan appeared at
OL,7,FNewcastle Crown Court where he pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to two counts of assault by
OL,9,Fpenetration, one count of non-fatal
OL,10,Fstrangulation, threats to kill and
OL,11,Fassault occasioning actual bodily harm.
OL,13,FHe was remanded in custody and was
OL,14,Fsentenced at the same court on Friday
OL,15,F(26 July) to 17 years in prison and a
OL,16,Ffurther four years on licence.
OL,18,FHe will also spend the rest of his
OL,19,Flife on the Sex Offenders' Register
OL,20,Fand was given a lifelong restraining
OL,21,Forder to protect the victim.
