OL,6,FDetective Constable Lucy Joyce, of
OL,7,FNorthumbria Police's Safeguarding
OL,8,FDepartment, led the investigation,
OL,9,Fsupported by Detective Constable
OL,10,FPhillip Trotter.
OL,12,FDet Con Joyce said: "Maughan preyed on
OL,13,Fthis woman, subjecting her to the most
OL,14,Fhorrendous physical and sexual abuse
OL,15,Fimaginable.
OL,17,F"I absolutely welcome this sentence
OL,18,Fand hope it provides his brave victim
OL,19,Fwith some comfort in knowing he's now
OL,20,Fbehind bars and will be for a long
OL,21,Ftime.
