OL,6,F"I want to praise her for her bravery
OL,7,Fand composure during the investigation
OL,8,Fand trial ` it is because of her
OL,9,Fcourage in coming forward that a
OL,10,Fdangerous man is locked up and will be
OL,11,Funable to hurt anyone else."
OL,13,FDet Con Trotter added: "I hope this
OL,14,Fconviction serves as a stark warning
OL,15,Fto those with a blurred view of
OL,16,Fconsent that someone consenting to
OL,17,Fmeet up with you or agreeing to go
OL,18,Fback to your room or home absolutely
OL,19,Fdoes not equate to sexual consent.
